        <prj:TechnicalJustification>
            <prj:justificationText>This program detects Quasi Periodic Oscillation (QPO) in the light curve of Sgr A* in Band 7. The amplitude of the QPO is expected to be 0.5%. Beacuse we search the QPO using Lomb periodgram method, the longer continuous light curve is better. The expected period of the QPO is about 30 min. Then 180-min monitor is required to detect it with reliability. And two day observation is necessary for the confirmation. </prj:justificationText>
        </prj:TechnicalJustification>
